snippet: An early start was pivotal as Britain's Danny Willett scorched his way to a seven-under-par 65 in the second round of the $2.5 million Dubai Desert Classic on Friday....

headline.print_headline: Early Riser Willett Avoids Wandering Mind in Dubai
headline.main: Early Riser Willett Avoids Wandering Mind in Dubai

lead_paragraph: An early start was pivotal as Britain's Danny Willett scorched his way to a seven-under-par 65 in the second round of the $2.5 million Dubai Desert Classic on Friday.
